    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, large dents, and widespread paint failure. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and persistent odors. Mechanically, the car requires major repairs to be reliably drivable.",
