    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for utility over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are functional and have been maintained to keep the car roadworthy, there are visible signs of wear consistent with its age. You should expect some minor cosmetic scratches on the exterior and some wear on the interior upholstery. All essential electronics are working, but the car lacks the polish of a newer model. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle for someone who needs reliable transportation at an affordable price.",
      "price": 21000.0,
