    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and reliable ride! It has been well-maintained and is in good condition, showing only minor signs of regular use that you'd expect from a well-loved vehicle. It drives smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy many more miles of dependable service. A great choice for anyone looking for a solid, high-quality vehicle that's ready to go!",
      "price": 34500.0,
