    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle that exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and sophisticated design. This unit has been carefully curated and maintains a high standard of mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. Rigorously inspected to ensure long-term reliability, it offers a premier driving experience for the discerning professional. Secure a vehicle that represents both a prudent investment and a testament to quality automotive care.",
      "price": 34900.0,
