      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive in Bluestone Metallic. This executive sedan has been a reliable daily driver and remains in great mechanical health. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power, and the all-wheel-drive system provides excellent confidence in all weather conditions. Inside, the Black Dakota leather interior is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster consistent with age. All electronics, including the iDrive infotainment and premium sound system, function perfectly. Externally, the paint retains a deep shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper. The car comes with a complete service history, including a recent oil change and brake inspection. It is a solid, honest vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
